{"tid":581794,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)極度深寒 無恐不入 剛果驚魂","createTime":"2018-03-05T15:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T20:56:56.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6977ad55d8615bcb631ef96eec14d217146fc4","tid":581794,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=DiGK16OJczRZvohM6yohsMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c468b0a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=DiGK16OJczRZvohM6yohsMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5257fd3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bd/Deep_rising_ver3.jpg/220px-Deep_rising_ver3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fbd%2FDeep_rising_ver3.jpg%2F220px-Deep_rising_ver3.jpg&h=799b686c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.rogerebert.com/uploads/movie/movie_poster/the-invasion-2007/large_AiGIhoLpX4gcbbaX6JwFSygAqPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rogerebert.com%2Fuploads%2Fmovie%2Fmovie_poster%2Fthe-invasion-2007%2Flarge_AiGIhoLpX4gcbbaX6JwFSygAqPY.jpg&h=6862cef5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img31.mtime.cn/mg/2013/05/05/175907.88976623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg31.mtime.cn%2Fmg%2F2013%2F05%2F05%2F175907.88976623.jpg&h=154df7f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一艘遊輪被貪婪噬血的怪物所盤據，受僱走私的約翰費尼根（崔特威廉斯飾）領隊的「塞班號」恰巧接近這艘郵輪，他的船員包括凱文歐康諾飾及大副萊拉（伍娜戴蒙飾）。當費尼根將他破損的「塞班號」停泊在「亞格遠征號」旁並攀爬上船時，發現處處都是遊輪遭到襲擊的痕跡，甲板上到處都是血，空氣凝重，靜默中充滿詭譎的氣氛..<br />\n<br />\n2.一艘發射沒多久的太空梭突然在空中解體，碎片掉落在美國德州到華盛頓州之間；這看似意外的太空梭的解體事故背後卻似乎隱藏者一個極大的陰謀。許多民眾在好奇的情況下去觸碰這些太空梭的碎片，甚至有人把撿到的太空梭碎片拿到eBay上面去賣，有一位名叫塔克（傑瑞米&middot;諾森飾演）的民眾也因此不小心被碎片割傷。而塔克在當天睡覺眼球快速轉動週期過後被細菌改變了其身體結構，隔天就變成被細菌完全控制的人<br />\n<br />\n3.一家公司派人到剛果尋找純度極高的鑽石，並將發現進行衛星傳送。但從尋像上看，那裡似乎發生了突發事件，似乎還看到某種體形巨大的動物。公司只好繼續派人到現場查明真相。靈長類動物學家彼得。埃利奧特帶著艾美&mdash;&mdash;一隻8歲的大猩猩前往。但是，熱帶雨林是另一個天地，在那裡主宰一切的可不是這些城市人的意志。這是一個表現人類和動物複雜關係的故事<br />\n<br />\n12 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=DiGK16OJczRZvohM6yohsMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=21b9fdab\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=DiGK16OJczRZvohM6yohsMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=97808716\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba172d48c8fdca791c2ff928e7bacfc43206170","tid":581794,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a881d9436970667681fca4ca72b0cc6ea16c25de","tid":581794,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":